name: Distributed SIP Analyzer
short_description:
Distributed SIP Analyzer is a SIP protocol analyzer for Unix.
It allows you to examine SIP from different local area network.
You can interactively browse the capture data, viewing callflow sequence diagram and detail information for each SIP Session.
